{"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"Sell a lifetime entitlement alongside a subscription and surface both flags through the paywall plugin.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"Overview","text":"Overview","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Many apps offer two ways to buy: a recurring pro subscription and a one-time lifetime purchase. RevenueCat models both as entitlements; ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"RevenueCatPaywallService"},{"text":" checks each independently and surfaces them as the two flags on ","type":"text"},{"code":"EntitlementSnapshot","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":":","type":"text"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"isPro","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" — active subscription."}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"hasPermanentLicense"},{"type":"text","text":" — active lifetime entitlement."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The paywall plugin’s ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isGateSatisfied"},{"text":" is ","type":"text"},{"code":"isPro || hasPermanentLicense","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", so feature code keeps a single check while UI can branch on the underlying flags when it needs to.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For the entitlement-mapping rules and edge cases, see ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/EntitlementMapping"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"anchor":"Before-you-start","type":"heading","text":"Before you start","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This guide assumes:","type":"text"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You have completed "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToImplementService","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You have configured ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"two"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" entitlements in the RevenueCat dashboard — typically ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"pro"},{"text":" for the subscription and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"lifetime"},{"text":" for the one-time purchase. The identifiers are arbitrary; only the strings need to match what you pass into the service.","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"anchor":"Step-1-Pass-the-second-identifier","text":"Step 1: Pass the second identifier","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Replace the single-entitlement init with the two-arg form:","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["import SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall","","let service = RevenueCatPaywallService(","    entitlementID: \"pro\",","    permanentLicenseEntitlementID: \"lifetime\"",")"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Both entitlements are now checked on every ","type":"text"},{"code":"customerInfo()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"code":"customerInfoStream()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" yield, and ","type":"text"},{"code":"restorePurchases()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" call. The active state of ","type":"text"},{"code":"pro","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" flows into ","type":"text"},{"code":"EntitlementSnapshot.isPro","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"; the active state of ","type":"text"},{"code":"lifetime","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" flows into ","type":"text"},{"code":"hasPermanentLicense","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The two flags are independent. A user with both active gets both flags set; a user with only one active gets only that flag set.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Step 2: Wire the service into the plugin","type":"heading","anchor":"Step-2-Wire-the-service-into-the-plugin"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Same as the single-entitlement case — the plugin doesn’t need to know about the second identifier:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["plugins.register(","    PaywallPlugin<AppState, AppAction>(","        state: \\.paywall,","        action: AppAction.paywall,","        extractAction: { if case .paywall(let a) = $0 { return a }; return nil },","        service: RevenueCatPaywallService(","            entitlementID: \"pro\",","            permanentLicenseEntitlementID: \"lifetime\"","        )","    )",")"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"level":2,"text":"Step 3: Decide whether feature code needs to branch","type":"heading","anchor":"Step-3-Decide-whether-feature-code-needs-to-branch"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"For most gated features, keep using ","type":"text"},{"code":"store.paywall.isGateSatisfied","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":":","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["if store.paywall.isGateSatisfied { … }"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This stays correct whether the user has a subscription or a lifetime license, and works identically in apps that don’t sell a lifetime SKU.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Step 4: Branch in UI when copy must differ","type":"heading","anchor":"Step-4-Branch-in-UI-when-copy-must-differ"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If the paywall sheet should be hidden for lifetime customers (so they’re not pestered to subscribe), or if the customer-center entry should be relabeled, branch on the underlying flag:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["if store.paywall.hasPermanentLicense {","    Text(\"Lifetime member — thank you!\")","} else if store.paywall.isPro {","    Button(\"Manage Subscription\") {","        store.send(.paywall(.presentCustomerCenter))","    }","} else {","    Button(\"Upgrade\") {","        store.send(.paywall(.request(reason: \"upgrade-prompt\")))","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Lifetime users typically have nothing to manage in App Store \/ Settings. Hiding the customer-center button for them avoids dead-end taps.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"When to skip the second identifier","type":"heading","anchor":"When-to-skip-the-second-identifier"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Pass ","type":"text"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" (or omit the parameter) if your app has no lifetime SKU:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["RevenueCatPaywallService(entitlementID: \"pro\")"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"code":"hasPermanentLicense","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" then stays ","type":"text"},{"code":"false","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" regardless of any entitlements RevenueCat reports — even if the dashboard accidentally has a ","type":"text"},{"code":"lifetime","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" entitlement that the service is not configured to check. See the ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Lifetime entitlement is ignored when no permanent-license ID is configured","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" test case for the precise behavior.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToAddAPermanentLicense","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"}],"roleHeading":"Article","role":"article","title":"How to Add a Permanent License"},"kind":"article","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall\/howtoaddapermanentlicense"]}],"seeAlsoSections":[{"title":"Related Documentation","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/ServiceReference","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/EntitlementMapping","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToImplementService"],"anchor":"Related-Documentation"},{"anchor":"How-to-Guides","generated":true,"title":"How-to Guides","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToImplementService","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToPresentTheUI","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToPreviewAndTest"]}],"references":{"doc://SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/documentation/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/ServiceReference":{"title":"Service Reference","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/ServiceReference","url":"\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall\/servicereference","abstract":[{"text":"API reference for ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"RevenueCatPaywallService"},{"text":" — the RevenueCat-backed ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallService"},{"text":" conformer that the paywall plugin consumes.","type":"text"}],"kind":"article","role":"article"},"doc://SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/documentation/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/HowToPresentTheUI":{"role":"article","kind":"article","abstract":[{"text":"Attach ","type":"text"},{"code":"PaywallSheet","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"code":"CustomerCenterSheet","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" from ","type":"text"},{"code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywallUI","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" to a root view, driven by ","type":"text"},{"code":"PaywallState","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToPresentTheUI","url":"\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall\/howtopresenttheui","title":"How to Present the UI","type":"topic"},"doc://SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/documentation/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/EntitlementMapping":{"role":"article","kind":"article","abstract":[{"text":"How RevenueCat’s ","type":"text"},{"code":"CustomerInfo.entitlements","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" translates to Swidux’s ","type":"text"},{"code":"EntitlementSnapshot","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/EntitlementMapping","url":"\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall\/entitlementmapping","title":"Entitlement Mapping","type":"topic"},"doc://SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/documentation/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/HowToPreviewAndTest":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Drive entitlement state from SwiftUI previews and tests with "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"MockRevenueCatPaywallService"},{"type":"text","text":" — no RevenueCat SDK call required."}],"url":"\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall\/howtopreviewandtest","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToPreviewAndTest","type":"topic","title":"How to Preview and Test","kind":"article","role":"article"},"doc://SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/documentation/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall":{"title":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall","url":"\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall","abstract":[{"text":"RevenueCat adapter for Swidux’s ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallPlugin"},{"text":". Implements ","type":"text"},{"code":"PaywallService","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" against ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Purchases.shared"},{"text":", ships a controllable mock for previews and tests, and pairs with ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywallUI"},{"text":" for drop-in ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallView"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomerCenterView"},{"type":"text","text":" presentation."}],"kind":"symbol","role":"collection"},"doc://SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/documentation/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/HowToImplementService":{"abstract":[{"text":"Wire ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"RevenueCatPaywallService"},{"text":" into the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SwiduxPaywall"},{"text":" plugin so the store sees real-time entitlement updates from RevenueCat.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","role":"article","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToImplementService","kind":"article","title":"How to Implement the Service","url":"\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall\/howtoimplementservice"}}}